            <description><![CDATA[<p>Release date: 2026-05-19</p>
<h2 id="new">New</h2>
<h2 id="improvements">Improvements</h2>
<ul>
<li><strong>Made credit updates more reliable for paid plans.</strong>
NameQuick now handles subscription credit renewals more consistently,
especially when account details arrive in stages.</li>
<li><strong>Improved credit status during account setup.</strong> Trial
and paid-plan setup now keep showing the right setup state while
NameQuick finishes checking your account.</li>
<li><strong>Made saved templates more reliable.</strong> Templates and
custom prompts are better protected during settings resets, so saved
naming workflows should remain available.</li>
</ul>
<h2 id="bug-fixes">Bug Fixes</h2>
<ul>
<li><strong>Fixed trial setup showing the wrong credit state.</strong>
Trial activation should now stay in the correct setup flow instead of
briefly showing unrelated credit or license messaging.</li>
<li><strong>Fixed paid credits sometimes appearing unavailable after
renewal.</strong> NameQuick now keeps checking the right account
information before deciding whether credits can be used.</li>
<li><strong>Fixed templates and custom prompts disappearing after a
reset.</strong> Saved naming templates and custom prompts should now
remain available instead of unexpectedly resetting.</li>
</ul>
]]></description>
